Chocolate Sheet Cake

3 c.- flour
2 c.- sugar
1/2 c.- 100% cocoa powder (dairy-free)
2 tsp- baking soda
1 tsp- salt
2 c.- water
2/3 c.- vegtable oil
2 tbsp- distilled white vinegar
2 tsp- vanilla extract
100% vegetable shortening

Use 100% vegetable shortening to grease and the flour a 13 by 9 inch pan.
In a large mixing bowl, combine flour, sugar, cocoa, baking soda, and salt.
Add water, oil, vinegar, and vanilla.
Beat with a spoon or wire whisk just until batter is smooth and al ingredients are well-blended.
Pour batter into prepared pan.
Bake in oven at 350 degrees for about 35 minutes or until done.
Let cool in pan for 10 minutes before turning out to cool completely.
Frost.